<p><a name="Name" id="Name"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mongol_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Name">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Name</span></h2>
<p>The Mongol Empire is translated to the <a href="/wiki/Mongolian_language" title="Mongolian language">Mongolian language</a> as "Mongolyn Ezent Guren" (Монголын эзэнт гүрэн) literally meaning "Mongols' Imperial Power" and "Ikh Mongol Uls" (Их Монгол улс) which literally means "<a href="/wiki/Greater" title="Greater">Greater</a> Mongol Nation/State." Both of these names are used.</p>
<p><a name="Political_history" id="Political_history"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mongol_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Political history">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Political history</span></h2>
<p><a name="Formation" id="Formation"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Mongol_Empire&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Formation">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Formation</span></h3>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:147px;"><a href="/wiki/File:YuanEmperorAlbumGenghisPortrait.jpg" class="image" title="Genghis Khan's picture at the National Palace Museum in Taipei, Taiwan"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/35/YuanEmperorAlbumGenghisPortrait.jpg/145px-YuanEmperorAlbumGenghisPortrait.jpg" width="145" height="184" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:YuanEmperorAlbumGenghisPortrait.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
