<td width="35%">
<p><b>Asia</b><br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Mongol_invasion_of_Central_Asia" title="Mongol invasion of Central Asia">Invasion of Central Asia</a></b><br />
<b><a href="/wiki/Mongol_invasion_of_East_Asia" title="Mongol invasion of East Asia">Invasion of East Asia</a></b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Genghis_Khan" title="Genghis Khan">1205–1209 Western China</a></li>
